<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>WHO ARE THESE?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chunglama kingkang gihawih tawh,
 Lasa kuote ahiu em?
 Ngaiun hehpihna a gen ui,
 Jehovah hehpih lopi.

[V2]
 &quot;Belam No thisan thienga,
 A puonsilh uh sawpa, thiengte ahiu&quot;
 &quot;Belam No thisan thienga,
 A puonsilh uh sawpa, thiengte ahiu&quot;

[V3]
 2. Kumsawt Lalchutphah kimvela,
 Um zingte kuote ahim?
 Lei a thawkgimna thuokzo a,
 Van chawlhna tungte a hiu.

[V4]
 3. Enun, a puon vamuh minthang,
 Nin beklo leh buokna bei;
 Enun, a Lallukhuk vam uh,
 Thahsa Belam No chawksa.

[V5]
 4. Pathien Belam No-in A pui,
 Sun, zan A na a sem ui;
 Van tuikhuk in amau A vak,
 A mitthiu A thiek hul tai.

[V6]
 5. A la thupiu zie ahi zing,
 &quot;Hukdamna Krista kawmah;&quot;
 Gimthuoka a maunau haw cheng,
 Lalchutphah kim' la'n a sau.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>376</hymn_number>
</song>